/* Configuración  visual code
File --> Autosave

Djaneiro - Django Snippets
Configuracion 
m + tab : usa los snippets del modelo
fk + tab: usa los snippets Foreing Key
f + tab: usa los snippets del formulario

Configuracion 
Material icon theme
file --> preferences --> file icon theme --> material icon

Configuracion 
Prettier - Code Formatter:
file --> preferences --> settings --> text Editor --> Code Actions On Save --> Edit in settings.json

------------------- Multiple Selection :https: //code.visualstudio.com/docs/editor/codebasics
ctrl + Shift + alt + up : selecciona campos desde el teclado
shift + alt :seleccionar con el mouse los campos

*/
{
  "terminal.integrated.shell.windows": "C:\\Program Files\\Git\\bin\\bash.exe",
  "workbench.colorTheme": "Monokai",
  "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
  "files.autoSave": "afterDelay",
  "editor.formatOnPaste": true,
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "[html]": {
    "editor.formatOnSave": true,
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "vscode.html-language-features" /* Aumenta la tabulación*/
  }
}
